+        Position2: Code[10];
+    begin
+        // [SCENARIO] When same item appears twice in Production BOM with different Position values,
+        // comments are correctly transferred to corresponding Prod Order Component lines based on Position.
+        // This tests the fix where the Position filter was added to CopyProdBOMComments in CarryOutAction codeunit.
+        Initialize();
